\v 2 Rhih boeh cawh uh laeh tholh hno sai thai nah te,
\q1 Tu ca caem puei he tah dal mah pawh tholh neh duek khui ah,
\q1 Hmai lam kah kho hmuep long he khaw cing boei coeng,
\q1 Zion kho puei tueng coeng dan uh lah,
\b
